sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as User SPA
  participant A as FastAPI
  participant ML as ml_engine
  participant DB as PostgreSQL
  participant P as Prometheus

  U->>A: POST /api/v1/evaluate {project}
  A->>ML: ensemble.predict_proba(X)
  ML-->>A: {proba, model_versions, shap}
  A->>DB: INSERT into PredictionLog
  A->>P: histogram sora_prediction_latency_ms.observe()
  A->>P: counter sora_predictions_total.inc()
  A-->>U: {esg_score, risk, explanation}
  Note over A,DB: drift_service.observe(X) writes to buffer
